==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: leaf roller
<hw>leaf roller</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The larva of any tortricid moth which makes a
nest by rolling up the leaves of plants and tying the leaves with spun
silk; aalso, the moth itself. See <er>Tortrix</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Leafstalk</ent>⟦br⟧
